bug on batik SVG DOM implementation on the SVGPathSegCurvetoCubicSmoothAbs

the SVGPathSegCurvetoCubicSmoothAbs method setX2() is not correct, the value set
is not same with the value from getX2()
after see the code the fix may be like below (based on batik 1.5beta5)

on the package org.apache.batik.dom.svg;

class AbstractSVGPathSegList.SVGPathSegCurvetoCubicSmoothItem

line 808 this.x1 = x2;  // suppose this.x2 = x2;


public void setX2(float x2){
            //this.x1 = x2;
            this.x2 = x2;
            resetAttribute();
        }
